\n<Eury>If there's anything you'd like to ask of a modified girl,
please feel free!
\n<Master>Would you like to work at my tavern, if it's okay with you?

bring in more customers! Please!

increase the number of visitors, huh?)

Marion, but I wonder if I'll be okay?)

rest.
Should I help out at the tavern?

want to work here.

\n<Eury>(...N-No, it's not like I'm expecting that! I just want to

treated you like that...

\n<Master>Alright, it's about time to open up!

\n<Master>Thanks to you, we're thriving. I'll be counting on you
again.
